ActCanada Infrastructure Bank Act
PrecisAppointment of MICHAEL J. BERNSTEIN of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Infrastructure Bank, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of James Charles Cherry, whose term has expired.
